{"tid":352012,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣遊客嫌香港唔好玩唔係一兩單","createTime":"2017-08-08T13:15:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-08T13:58:35.000Z","uid":16970,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dc02a2c6ae17472f7025e0b8cce25758a8335a98","tid":352012,"uid":16970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T13:15:56.000Z","msg":"今日有單台灣遊客嫌香港唔好玩嘅新聞，成為網上熱話，唔少香港人走出嚟話依名台灣男子唔識貨。但係，恐怕唔係剩係依名台灣男子係咁諗。<br />\n<br />\n睇番旅遊業市場數據，今年六月台灣訪港旅客人次，比上年同期少咗成７．１％，如果剩係計過夜客嘅話就仲誇張，比上年同期跌咗１５．１％。數字唔呃人嘅話，咁就證明咗香港對台灣遊客嘅吸引力下跌的確係事實。<br />\n<br />\n睇怕旅遊業界嘅人士要認真諗諗計了。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果日報報導：<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170808/57053957\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170808%2F57053957&d=%2BvpOqeBWzixi1gP9YfE2gfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=2b23b8b8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170808%2F57053957&h=bd4eb2c1\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170808/57053957</a><br />\n旅遊發展局１７年６月訪港旅客人次統計資料：<a href=\"http://partnernet.hktb.com/filemanager/intranet/pm/VisitorArrivalStatistics/ViS_Stat_C/ViS_C_2017/Tourism%20Statistics%2006%202017.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpartnernet.hktb.com%2Ffilemanager%2Fintranet%2Fpm%2FVisitorArrivalStatistics%2FViS_Stat_C%2FViS_C_2017%2FTourism%2520Statistics%252006%25202017.pdf&d=%2BvpOqeBWzixi1gP9YfE2gfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=4f99fc8b\" target=\"_blank\">http://partnernet.hktb.com/filemanager/intranet/pm/VisitorArrivalStatistics/ViS_Stat_C/ViS_C_2017/Tourism%20Statistics%2006%202017.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/20663603_1930385997201245_1326323178552602698_n.png?oh=224b7ea2b246aaac20ddc7a08b720a1a&amp;oe=5A34BFC0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F20663603_1930385997201245_1326323178552602